<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;&nbsp;For&nbsp;those&nbsp;who&nbsp;want&nbsp;the&nbsp;easy&nbsp;way</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;have&nbsp;some&nbsp;implications</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>This is the birth of Foundation Classic (something I will expand upon in the future), with the simultaneous discovery of 173 and Site-19 (now 001-ARC). Everyone mentioned in this story is part of the senior staff: Francis is Clef (before he is Clef), Jack is Bright (before he's immortal), Agatha is Rights, Connor is Gears, Adam is Kain pre-dogification, Dmitri is Strenilkov (before he sorta loses it) John is Yoric, Ben is Kondraki, Nemo is Nobody (I would have made him Fish, but that was most likely a really bad idea), and Fats is A Fat Ghost. That's ten of the twelve O5s (e: in this particular universe).</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>For those who enjoyed this, I can safely say that Francis and company will be returning in the future.</p>

